    <item>
      <title>Bofa的Hartnett：DeepSeek在我们AI故事中引起了顶峰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/bofa-s-hartnett-deepseek-caused-a-peak-in-us-ai-story-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席投资策略师迈克尔·哈特内特（Michael Hartnett）表示，中国迪斯特（Deepseek）的到来暂时在AI故事中造成了高峰，并从美国技术转移到了中国技术。哈特内特（Hartnett）在迪拜的美国银行投资者峰会上与彭博（Bloomberg）的盖伊·约翰逊（Guy Johnson）进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/bofa-s-hartnett-deepseek-caused-a-peak-in-us-ai-story-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯提供中东的第一个欧元绿色债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/saudi-arabia-offers-middle-east-s-first-euro-green-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯开始出售以欧元计价的绿色债券，这是该地区一项主权的第一笔交易，因为它希望为王国雄心勃勃的经济转变计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/saudi-arabia-offers-middle-east-s-first-euro-green-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区工资增长从记录中降温，支持欧洲央行削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/euro-zone-wage-growth-cools-from-record-backing-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲地区薪酬增长的关键衡量标准在2024年底降低了，支持欧洲中央银行计划随着通货膨胀速度的减慢降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/euro-zone-wage-growth-cools-from-record-backing-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国银行负责人希望新德国政府迅速成立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bundesbank-chief-wants-new-german-government-formed-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据德省总裁约阿希姆·纳格尔（Joachim Nagel）称，德国政党应在周日大选后迅速组成新的政府，以防止经济连续第三年扩展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bundesbank-chief-wants-new-german-government-formed-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的纳格尔（Nagel）呼吁同事阻止率猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/ecb-s-nagel-calls-on-colleagues-to-halt-rate-cut-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据管理理事会成员Joachim Nagel称，欧洲中央银行官员将“很好”停止公开讨论他们的利率偏好，这是由于粘性通货膨胀和不确定性提高的偏好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/ecb-s-nagel-calls-on-colleagues-to-halt-rate-cut-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库集会随着交易者提高降低利率削减的赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/treasuries-rally-as-traders-boost-bets-on-fed-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易商提高对美联储利益率的押注，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税计划负担了风险的胃口，国库会集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/treasuries-rally-as-traders-boost-bets-on-fed-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 09:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
